message.body: Hey man, I'm trying to make some plans. Just a guess, what do you think the chances are of me getting stuck with that job again today is? ...just a guess.
Yesss! Awesome. Thanks. Hit me up if things change tho.
Word. Yeah last week my bike that can handle that load needed some repair. If ever I can't do it i'll text u early on
Ok. Is it ever ready before 6?
dunno, It's scheduled for 6 so they don't call when it is ready
